<section class="section">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-12 section-title">
				<h2>Top categories</h2>
				<h5>Selected Services", sub-headline to "Our convenient booking interface connects to our base of pre-selected providers for minimally invasive aesthetic procedures from the comfort of your home, office, or at the provider facility, seamlessly.</h5>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row top-categories-grid">
			<div class="col-sm-4" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path('categories/top-4.jpg') %>);">
				<div class="box-default">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<h3>Wrinkle Reduction</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="box-hover">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<p class="cat-title">Wrinkle Reduction</p>
						<div class="cat-descript">
							Facial wrinkles can be prevented with simple treatments with little
							to no downtime. Leading products such as Botox and Dysport can help
							to slow down the aging process through wrinkle reduction by temporarily
							weakening the muscles that cause the wrinkles to appear.
						</div>
						<%= link_to 'View doctors', doctors_path(speciality_id: 1), class: 'btn btn-border-white' %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path('categories/top-2.jpg') %>);">
				<div class="box-default">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<h3>Dermal Fillers</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="box-hover">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<p class="cat-title">Dermal Fillers</p>
						<div class="cat-descript">
							During the aging process volume loss of the face typically occurs.  This makes
							you appear tired and sad.  Dermal fillers are used to immediately enhance and
							restore lost volume and turn back the aging process.  Commonly treated areas
							are the cheeks, lips, temples, nasolabial folds, and jawline.
						</div>
						<%= link_to 'View doctors', doctors_path(speciality_id: 2), class: 'btn btn-border-white' %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path('categories/top-3.jpg') %>);">
				<div class="box-default">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<h3>Skin Treatments</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="box-hover">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<p class="cat-title">Skin Treatments</p>
						<div class="cat-descript">
							Multiple options exist to help eliminate fine lines and wrinkles of the face,
							as well as skin damage from sun exposure.  With the use of chemical peels,
							laser resurfacing, and micro-needling the aging process can be reversed.
						</div>
						<%= link_to 'View doctors', doctors_path(speciality_id: 3), class: 'btn btn-border-white' %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path('categories/top-3.jpg') %>);">
				<div class="box-default">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<h3>Non Surgical Fat Reduction</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="box-hover">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<p class="cat-title">Non Surgical Fat Reduction</p>
						<div class="cat-descript">
							Need to get rid of unwanted body fat and do not have the time for surgery?
							Try these modalities to lose a few inches for a slimmer you.
						</div>
						<%= link_to 'View doctors', doctors_path(speciality_id: 4), class: 'btn btn-border-white' %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path('categories/top-1.jpg') %>);">
				<div class="box-default">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<h3>Hair reduction</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="box-hover">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<p class="cat-title">Hair reduction</p>
						<div class="cat-descript">
							Do you have unwanted hair loss that you wish you could reverse.
							With minimal invasive procedures you can have a full head of hair in no time.
							These procedures are done with minimal anesthesia and require very little recovery.
						</div>
						<%= link_to 'View doctors', doctors_path(speciality_id: 5), class: 'btn btn-border-white' %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path('categories/top-5.jpg') %>);">
				<div class="box-default">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<h3>Cellulite and Vein Treatment</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="box-hover">
					<div class="vertical-align">
						<p class="cat-title">Cellulite and Vein Treatment</p>
						<div class="cat-descript">
							Are you looking to get rid of unsightly cellulite and prominent veins
							for a smooth leg appearance?  Multiple treatments options exist to
							help to maintain a youthful look and restore your skins appearance.
						</div>
						<%= link_to 'View doctors', doctors_path(speciality_id: 6), class: 'btn btn-border-white' %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="section feature-section">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-12 section-title">
				<h2>About Somlos</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-12 feature-carousel">
				<div class="feature-box">
					<div class="icon"><img src="<%= asset_path('icon-1.png') %>" alt="icon" width="90"></div>
					<h3>24/7 availability</h3>
					<div class="descript">
						<p>Simple, convenient, &amp; seamless. Schedule your appointment
							and treatment with the provider of your choice on your time.
							Be able to evaluate provider’s qualifications and track record
							with our dynamic review process.  See all availabilities across
							your location with geotargeting technology and choose ideal time
							slots and providers according to your schedule. </p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-box">
					<div class="icon"><img src="<%= asset_path('icon-2.png') %>" alt="icon" width="90"></div>
					<h3>Advanced technology</h3>
					<div class="descript">
						<p>Follow the latest trends and techniques in cosmetic surgery and
							how providers are using them to enhance overall results.
							See provider reviews and schedule your appointment.
							Be able to pay for service prior to your visit to have a seamless
							visit and cost savings via our rewards program.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-box">
					<div class="icon"><img src="<%= asset_path('icon-3.png') %>" alt="icon" width="90"></div>
					<h3>Qualified doctors</h3>
					<div class="descript">
						<p>Our base of providers perform procedures using state of the art equipment,
							board certified physicians and/or work with a board certified physician.
							Each provider must practice within their scope of care and pass the SÖMLÖS
							excellence of care to be selected as a SÖMLÖS provider.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="section">
